  <title>Chess engines</title>
  <p>Gnome-chess automatically detects chess engines installed in the system.
  To pick the chess engine you want to play against:</p>
  <steps>
    <item><p>Click <gui>Gnome-chess</gui> in the top bar and select
    <gui>Preferences</gui>.</p></item>
    <item><p>Select <gui style="tab">Game</gui>.</p></item>
    <item><p>Select a chess engine from the drop down list as the
    <gui>Opposing player</gui>.</p></item>
  </steps>
